  "title": "Senior Laboratory Officer (FAB Operation) (NSTIC), IME",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description:</u></p><p>Be part of an exciting FAB Operations Team working on cutting-edge process technologies.<br />This position is based in Singapore.</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Looking for reliable individual - Operate multiple type of semiconductor equipment in cleanroom environment.</li><li>Ability to use computer-based programs and applications to perform daily work/duties.</li><li>Operate equipment based on the required process specifications (e.g. procedures, change notifications, \netc.).</li><li>Participate actively and be responsible in assigned on-the-job assignments and other required trainings when \nrequested.</li><li>Provide machine operations coverage and backup supports when necessary.</li><li>Adequate understanding of the Equipment in-charge, monitor performance, timely communication with \nEngineers-in-charge to perform equipment errors recovery promptly when necessary.</li><li>Demonstrate excellent teamwork to promptly execute process sequences and data collections if \nrequired.</li><li>Always follow safety protocols & rules in the Clean Room.</li><li>Ensure 6S in the work environment and promptly report hazards/ suspicious/ abnormal activities or \npersonnel if any identified.</li><li>Address potential areas for improvements such as wafers processing cycle time, Equipment utilization, \nSafety/ Compliances, and cost savings.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Experience:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in MicroElectronics/Electrical/Mechanical/Chemical Engineering.</li><li>Basic understanding on semiconductor process is preferred.</li><li>1-3 years of experience in semiconductor processes (Photolithography, Dry/Wet Etch/Cleans,ThinFilms, \nDiffusions, Chemical mechanical Polishings, Metrology etc.) will be added advantages.</li><li>Must be a self-starter, dependable and highly motivated.</li></ul><p><strong>The above eligibility criteria are not exhaustive. A*STAR may include additional selection criteria based on its prevailing recruitment policies. These policies may be amended from time to time without notice. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
